{
  "stem": "8786.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The place was not for making parties.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What I do remember is that anything like a Purim or a Simchat Torah which was celebrated by the community-- it was in the private homes of better or the well to do people.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that goes-- even my father had in our own home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember it was a party.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] I also remember my own bar mitzvah, which was held in my own-- in my own-- in my our-- in my home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because there was no such thing like a catered affair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Everything was done homemade.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Unfortunately, by the time I became bar mitzvah, I prepared a beautiful speech.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I still remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was in the late summer in August.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember even the parashah of the-- of the-- of the Sidra.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was Shoftim.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Unfortunately, by the time my turn came, half of the town's Jewish men were already called in for forced labor, because this was in 1940.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was born in '27, and 13 years later came 1940.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And just a few weeks before my bar mitzvah celebration was supposed to come up, half of the schul was empty.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I still had my drosha here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My speech is still here with me, which I only said it to the close family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was a very-- it was-- in Yiddish they say it, [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was-- it turned out-- turned out a sour one because many people were called away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This is about-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we also were very, very-- my sister and brothers were very active.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And my father was a very popular man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I will never forget that, even though today, it's not customary.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
